Hello January! Guess who is back for another year? #juststartletteringchallenge is back and this month without one of our favorite cohosts. I really went back and forth on taking a month off but since it is the new year, I felt inspired. This month, I encourage you to join me in lettering ‘Word of the Year.’ What will your word of the year be? ✨
.
.
.
.
For those of you that are new, this challenge is to encourage new and experienced lettering artists to share their lettering journey with us through our positive and motivational prompts. Don’t be shy! Just start lettering with us & everyone is welcome to join in.

Remember to tag us @asklettering and use the hashtag #JustStartLetteringChallenge so that we can see your amazing work!
.
